OL,12,CG2000FThe first edition of Liquid News
OL,13,Fairs on BBC Choice. The programme was a
OL,14,Fnightly round-up of the day's
OL,15,Fentertainment news, originally
OL,16,Fpresented by Christopher Price, until
OL,17,Fhis death, aged 34, on 22nd April 2002.
